column5: He, just wondering what the waves will be like in the perch areas on the north end tomorrow. They are calling for 21 km south winds.
21km/h from the south?  I wouldn't want to be up there, it will be rockin' and rollin' for sure.
go into the south part of Couch.
I was thinking couch would be a safer bet.

My rule of thumb is I won't go out in anything more then a 15km north or south wind, or a 20km east or west wind on Cooks. Just not worth it for a few fish. I've had some scary trips going back across in high winds.
